text: Gizo/Kolombangarqa is a constituency of the Solomon Islands. It is in the Western Province. It was created in 1976. ==Election results== 2019 general election Candidate Party Votes Lanelle Olandrea Tanangada Kadere Party 4,397 Gordon Darcy Llio Party for Rural Advancement 4,002 John Hopa Independent 103 Invalid/blank votes 30 Total 8,532 Registered voters 10,527 Source: Solomon Islands Electoral Commission ==References== Category:Solomon Islands parliamentary constituencies
title: Gizo/Kolombangara constituency
